Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we just shelve\Nall the books
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in the library a few\Nmonths ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but that was\Nbecause we needed to;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,this is just\Nbecause I want to:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it my\Nbooksortcation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Three uninterrupted days\Nof re-organizing books!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you think of\Nanything more relaxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, claw massages, back\Nrubs, bubble baths...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't really looking\Nfor an answer, were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've even devised a better\Nsystem for organizing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It decreases the amount of\Ntime it takes to find the book
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're looking for by\Nnearly 3/4 of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why there must be at least\N20,000 books to organize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Best long weekend ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can make some\Ntime for a claw massage
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and a back rub, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Best long weekend ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles by YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that strange yellow\Norb in the sky! What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's been a little while\Nsince we've seen the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been in that library\Nfor 3 straight days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! But they were three\Nvery productive days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you did take that\Ntwo-hour claw massage break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You promise a claw massage?\NI'm getting a claw massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we\Nmissed anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you rehearse\Nbefore you found us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you\Nthink we practiced?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Rainbow Dash.\NWhat's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, me and Discord are\Njust messin' around. Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight, we've simply\Nhad a momentous time together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,these past three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say it was\Nhisss-sterical! Ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha! Sneaky Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo hoo hoo! Just\Nsnaking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good one, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of an inside joke\Nfrom this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't really get\Nit unless you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool. Well, uh, catch\Nyou later, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch you later, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That was strange, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when have Rainbow Dash\Nand Discord had "inside jokes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Since sometime in the\Nlast three days, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Nopony made you join\Nme on my booksortcation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joking. I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! You've returned from\Nyour book-sorting sabbatical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All that organizing has done\Nwonders for your complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. It was\Nvery relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were able\Nto clear a shelf
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,for those old-fashioned\Nbooks you wanted to donate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not old, darling;\Nthey're vintage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're over there. I've\Neven included my favorites
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,by former Canterlot Designer\Nto the stars, Rococo Froufrou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, ha. Both.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes twice I'm seeing you\Nin one day. Aren't I lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you just with--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Twilight! Hi, Spike!\NHow was your booksortcation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Orange you glad\Nyou did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Orange" you glad! Fluttershy,\Nyou're a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, you'll make me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You do seem to be turning\Na shade of orange!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, darling. You see, we\Nwere at Sweet Apple Acres...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And oh, how to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me try and paint\Nher a picture, dearest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dearest?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we were all\Nat Sweet Apple Acres
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ended up turning\Nthe trees into the most--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply can't do it justice.\NYou really had to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We would have invited\Nyou to come along too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but we didn't want to\Ninterrupt your organizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We know how important\Nit is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure it was\Nmuch more important
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,than the fun that we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of books, I should\Nget these on the shelves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, Rainbow Dash\Nbonding with Discord;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity finding something\Nhe did genuinely funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Must have been some weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony sorry she missed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got you two\Nin hysterics?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we were just reminiscing\Nabout the best weekend ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's everywhere\Ntoday, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, now where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, we'd just finished our\Nsoup and then Applejack said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Peanut butter hoof? Yuck!\NNot even with jelly."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hilarious. I wish we'd\Ntaken a picture for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well\Nthis should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:07:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, seems this has become\Nquite the sticky situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,HA! Sticky situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw shucks, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't even asked\Nhow your weekend went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet you look so glum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Does somepony need\Na huggy-wuggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoooo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not glum. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you all had such\Na good time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Having inside jokes can\Nreally create a lasting bond
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,between friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just sorry that all\Nthis bonding happened
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,while you were holed\Nup in your castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you worry\N'bout Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet you were in hog heaven\Norganizin' all them books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I had just as much\Nfun as the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I missed\Nout on all that bonding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! You are jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm the Princess of\NFriendship. I don't get jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I missed out because\Nsharing that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,would have helped me with my\NPrincess of Friendship duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If our friends could enjoy\Nthree full days with Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that much, it must have\Nsomething to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the specific things\Nthey did together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could find out\Nwhat those things were,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be a real breakthrough\Nin the science of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know so! You thought our\Nbooksortcation was fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be\Neven better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have asked you\Nhere if it wasn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I love important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know how these "funny"\Nmoments you shared came to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use this data to\Nhelp advance friendships
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,all over Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect. Let's start\Nwith, "The Snake."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can get\Nit out! It's too funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but we must. It's\Nfor the greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It started when we were helping\NGranny Smith with her garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I reckon you mean\Nmy sister, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. All you Apples\Nlook the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Rainbow\NDash saw a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a garden hose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a "Hose\NSnake." Super Deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall it being a large stick
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that looked like a hose\Nthat in turn did in fact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,resemble a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Point is WE galloped away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And it chased after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The hose? A snake? A stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A hose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We literally trotted for our\Nlives. Isn't that hilarious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you had to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I DO need to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's already happened.\NOooh. Are you suggesting--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Time Travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not! Time travel is\Nnot something to be messed with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We simply need to\Nrecreate everything
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that led to these jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What a brilliant idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin with the\Nlunch date that kicked off
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the glorious weekend\Nyou missed out on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was this table?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, does it really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to science,\Neverything matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One change to the equation\Ncould ruin the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhhhh. It was this table here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so you\Nsat down at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well first, I\Nexpressed my displeasure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,with the design\Nof the menu and--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry to interrupt, but\NI've just noticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The tablecloth. It\Nisn't the same color
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,as the one the restaurant\Nused on the day in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. The\Ntablecloth was red.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember because it clashed\Nwith the font on the menus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose that\Nmeans we're gonna need
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to get a new\Ntablecloth, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, most definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One change to the equation\Ncould ruin the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight said so herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything stand out as being\Ndifferent? Anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I've noticed a\Ncouple of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A little to the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,no, my left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a little bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,oh no, no, no, a\Nlittle more right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The cloud over our table looked\Nlike an ice cream sundae.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No. No. No. No. This is\Nbarely room temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Garcon! Garcon, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure there's not\Nsomething you've missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Some other detail about\Nyour lunch together
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're forgetting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know\Nabout the rest of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel we've been pretty\Nexhaustive in our attempts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to recreate every single detail\Nof our previous encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Twilight. If you\Ndon't get it by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're\Never gonna get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is really important\Nthat I figure this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the good\Nof all Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, perhaps we should\Nhave another look
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at the data we've collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one last variable\Nthat we haven't accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't there observing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard we try,\Nwe can't possibly recreate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,our weekend of fun\Nexactly as it happened
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because you'll always be\Nwatching and you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It has only served to prove that\Nmoments of levity and bonding
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,between friends simply\Ncannot be recreated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so that others might\Nshare in the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes another good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry, darling;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there'll be plenty of\Nother chances for you to share
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kind of frivolity\Nwe had with Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,while you were away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And I'll bet they'll\Nbe just as...hissssterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not buying it.\NNot for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is definitely something\Nelse going on here, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe there isn't\Nand you should just drop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,this whole thing and admit\Nthat you're a little jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm not able to\Nlaugh at what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to figure\Nout why they find it funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why they think they had\Nthis amazing and hilarious
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't figure it out.\NIt doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things just\Ncan't be explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friends think something\Ngreat happened to them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,while I was away. But no!\NIt was something awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't break the\Nspell they're under,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows what terrible\Nthings could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike! There's\Nno time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora, what do you think?\NCan you undo Discord's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way can you tell that\Nthey are indeed under a spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're having fun with\NDiscord; that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, a friendship with\NDiscord is truly a shock
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but who says it is something\Nthat we must block?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, they would\Nnever laugh like that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,unless something magical was\Ninvolved. It's not that funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this potion\Nwill break the spell
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,then you will be able to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, if that's the potion, then\Nwhat's brewing in your cauldron?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It ties the room together\Nand emits a warm glow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I am to be honest,\Nit's just for show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why she asked us\Nhere so bright and early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Another map adventure perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. No glowing tushies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's more of\Na non-adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she just wants to tell us\Nhow last night's slumber went.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you look excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am excited! We're\Ngonna have fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one tiny, miniscule,\Nmicroscopic thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,before fun times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I need everypony\Nto sip this potion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to break Discord's spell on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be embarrassed. So what\Nif Discord cast a spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so you THOUGHT you\Nhad a great time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you have all\Nthese inside jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that you seem to be\Nconstantly laughing at.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you didn't have\Nyour defenses up; I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, darling, we simply\Nhad a nice time with Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall, we spent much\Nof yesterday afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,re-enacting it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Or you re-enacted\Nwhat you thought was fun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but really wasn't because\Nyou were under a spell
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that made you think\Nwhat happened was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of fertilizer have\Nyou had your nose in, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest; the only reason\Nyou won't drink the potion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is because deep down in your\Nhearts you know there's a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that Discord has\Nyou under his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! How could\Nyou say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Discord still\Nmakes mistakes sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're accusing him\Nof being downright evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And to top it\Noff, you're accusing us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of not being able to tell\Nhe was up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you take us for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What do\Nyou... take us for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious! Got any\Nmore, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The gang mentioned we'd all be\Nhanging out together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the peanut\Nbutter hoof gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for that\Nwhole spell theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! It's still not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny if you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't there!\NI wasn't included.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's my own\Nfault for staying in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and having a booksortacation\Nwhen I could have been
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,making jokes and memories\Nwith my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't do that,\Ndid I? You all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You were all there but--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't there. I missed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And seeing you having all\Nthese jokes I wasn't a part of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and couldn't\Nunderstand made me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No. The Princess of\NFriendship can't get jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you can, Twilight. And\Nnone of us begrudge you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry if we made\Nyou feel left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're allowed to share\Nthings that don't include me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're allowed to feel\Na little jealous about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to be able to\Nadmit that's what you're feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, not try to\Nmake us recreate everything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that happened when\Nyou weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, none of this\Nwould have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if I hadn't encouraged everypony\Nnot to invite you this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanted me to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you convinced\Nthem to not invite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't think that\Nthey should interrupt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I see that we should\Nhave. Oh, I feel just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like\Nyou feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't suggest\Nnot inviting Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,cause you wanted to make\Nher feel left out, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That whole jealousy thing\Nwas just a happy accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly we can all agree\Nthat Princess Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,learned a valuable lesson here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That even she can have\Nfeelings of jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That she should\Nrecognize said feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than try to pretend\Nthat she doesn't have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get the tiniest bit\Nof glee out of watching her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,try to recreate our weekend of\Nfun in the name of "science"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, most definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's important here is\Nthat it was never my intent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to make Twilight feel jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something the old\Nme would have tried to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Orange you glad I've changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "Orange you\Nglad I've changed?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Orange! Like the ones\Nat the Applejack farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,From this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Nothing? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd find\Nthis hisss-sterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no. Discord, I think these\Njokes have run their course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Only way we'd find\Nthem funny now is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,if you put us all under\Nsome kind of spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You'd have to\Nbe a complete crazy pony
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to think he'd do\Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going\Nto say next, Pinkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That we'd all have to drink some\Nweird potion to break the spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Discord, do we really\Nhave to spell it out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony want to tell me\Nwhat's so hilarious? Anypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? I'm talking to\Nyou! You and you, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's funny about spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it; I feel left out\Nand I feel really bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, buddy. Guess\Nyou had to be there.
